Package algorithms.util

Class LinkedListCostNode

java.lang.Object
algorithms.util.SimpleLinkedListNode
algorithms.util.LinkedListCostNode
public class LinkedListCostNode extends SimpleLinkedListNode
extends SimpleLinkedListNode to hold an integer for the cost (which is by default Integer.MAX_VALUE for use with min heaps and priority queues). (NOTE, could edit the code to make defaultCost modifiable.)
Author:
nichole
